ensibility can result in new revenue streams and increased user engagement.\n* A platform can work closely with ISVs to understand their needs, build the necessary integrations, and provide the tools and documentation needed for easy development and deployment of new solutions on the platform.\n* By prioritizing extensibility and working closely with ISVs, a platform can create a more collaborative and productive partnership, resulting in a better user experience for their customers."]

